rComments: He's very intense and kind of an awkward guy, but he really loves the subject.  He has interesting lectures and is very animated.  He seems rude at first but I think it's just that he is blunt.  If you go to his office hours he is happy to work with you for hours.  Secretly he's nice and cares!
Good professor, cares a lot. His tests are very similar to the practice tests he suggests. Very sassy.
